overview: Tim Dolan joined FishNet Security in 2005. Mr. Dolan is a certified public accountant with over 23 years of professional experience. Prior to joining FishNet Security, Mr. Dolan was CFO for US Salt Holdings, LLC. where he was one of the original founders. Between 1993 and 1997, Mr. Dolan held various corporate finance positions with Harris Chemical Group, Inc. and GS Technologies., and prior to that, Mr. Dolan served ten years in the audit department of Ernst & Young, LLP. Mr. Dolan is a graduate of the University of Missouri-Kansas City.
